The organisers of the Big Brother Naijs reality tv show has officially opened the doors for the general public to audition for the seventh season of the show. This was disclosed in a tweet, urging interested Nigerian youths to be the next reality tv Star. The tweet read, “Biggie is calling you back home. -Advertisement- “#BBNaija Season 7 auditions are officially open, are you the next Efe, Miracle, Mercy, Laycon or Whitemoney? “This is your time to show Biggie what you’re all about  audition here: africamagic.tv/bbaudition. Audition now!”